            <thetext>If a decorator is referred to in a decoration theme, which is not included in the build, a fallback decorator (Uniform) is used.
This leads to unclear errors and warnings messages because Uniform decorator does not support some of the properties being used or even expects different parameter types (e.g. string instead of list for color).

A class not found exception would be more expressive here.</thetext>
